The absolute best is Hitman Hart:  Wrestling With Shadows.  However, if you want the newest interviews with Bret along with some of the best footage you can see of him from his early Stampede days to WCW, this is the DVD to get!  I'm so glad to finally have some excellent matches of his on DVD.  My only complaint was the audio on the Hart vs. Austin match for Wrestlemania 13 is off by about 2 seconds which doesn't sound like much but is very noticeable when someone hits the mat and there's no sound until a few seconds later.  But it's not enough to drop it down to 4 stars.  

