They did an excellent job with this DVD despite the fact McMahon had to give a BS statement at the beginning about Bret 
"putting their differences aside" for the sake of the DVD.  It was very obviously another dig by an unscrupulous shyster.

If you're looking for the "Montreal Screwjob" match in its entirety on this DVD, you won't find it.  It was cut for time (and Bret said he wanted to "de-emphasize" it on this project) but is featured in bits and pieces in the documentary itself.  Thankfully Bret hocking on McMahon was shown several times which made me smile after the opening statement by McMahon.

Highly recommended
